{"tid":774930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"競選時的承諾：特朗普說到做到了嗎？BBC","createTime":"2018-08-10T17:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T16:29:08.000Z","uid":50457,"like":61,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5655cc60dfd88a764cb80799bcd71f24fad042bc","tid":774930,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/world-39702333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fworld-39702333&d=64OpQCPjQvKxXoztncByBtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0badeee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/world-39702333</a><br />\n<br />\n外交政策<br />\n在競選期間，特朗普的外交政策視野是一系列有時矛盾、經常具有爭議的提案。<br />\n<br />\n參選時的他說過要對所謂的「伊斯蘭國」以及伊朗和中國採取強硬措施，重申了與以色列的同盟關係，修補與俄羅斯的關係。他有念頭要解除對虐囚的禁令，並且給予美軍更多行動的權力，包括將懷疑武裝分子的家人列為目標。<br />\n<br />\n他承諾將美國放在第一位，並且談化對美國盟友以及他認為負擔過大的國際聯盟的支持。<br />\n<br />\n作為總統， 矛盾的性質可能已經改變，但是爭議則是繼續存在。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普與習近平再次通話<br />\n特朗普：朝鮮曾屬中國<br />\n特朗普簽署行政命令決定美國退出TPP<br />\n會晤習近平後特朗普&quot;食言&quot;：中國非匯率操縱國<br />\n他將美國從跨太平洋伙伴關係（TPP）中拉走，並開始重新審視北美自由貿易協定（North American Free Trade Agreement）。<br />\n<br />\n多虧了國防部長詹姆斯&middot;馬蒂斯（James Mattis）的影響，虐囚仍然不被允許。特朗普有時候向外國領導人&mdash;&mdash;比如德國總理安格拉&middot;默克爾（Angela Merkel）和意大利總理保羅&middot;詹蒂洛尼（Paolo Gentiloni）&mdash;&mdash;說他期望他們增加軍費開支。另一方面，他最近也承認了北約成員資格的價值。<br />\n<br />\n不過，在中國的問題上，他卻採取了更柔和的路線。他不再遵守承諾，將中國列為「匯率操縱國」，也不再強行增加關稅，反而在處理朝鮮問題上尋求中國的幫助。<br />\n<br />\n然後，特朗普又在敘利亞政府對它的平民使用化學武器之後下令空襲該國。這是特朗普在參選時可能會標籤為&quot;無效&quot;的那一類行動&mdash;&mdash;事實上，在2013年奧巴馬提出介入敘利亞問題時，當時作為電視真人秀明星的特朗普也曾毫不含糊地遣責過。<br />\n<br />\n說到做到了？ 是，不是，或許。你可以自行判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e999514a571eeaa16c873e902c18398037b7126","tid":774930,"uid":4783,"like":175,"dislike":4,"score":171,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"有時真係駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n單計競選承諾應該近年無任何一個總統deliver到比佢更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6671186068c9c63372b462a1c037c9c325590f6f","tid":774930,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0092ba81f68e47f7db347544d672f794521e6bc","tid":774930,"uid":104699,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"言必信，行必果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4beb69c0c96d8497a043c51d6408bdc9d35d0093","tid":774930,"uid":121146,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"言出必行 大總統風範"},{"pid":"ccae3b9e0aaa52190e899c6eea9ad6bc0c0d4b73","tid":774930,"uid":50457,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"屈宏斌：特朗普對中國進口徵收&ldquo;45%關稅&rdquo;的影響有多大<br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行大中華區首席經濟學家屈宏斌認為，45%的進口關稅可能導致中美雙邊貿易額大幅下降，但對中國整體出口的影響則相對可控。中國政府可能會採取報復性貿易政策應對，並導致部分美國出口產品失去中國市場。中國未來可能更多轉向與其他新興市場地區的貿易和投資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://xw.qq.com/iphone/m/caijingzhiku/23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxw.qq.com%2Fiphone%2Fm%2Fcaijingzhiku%2F23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html&d=64OpQCPjQvKxXoztncByBtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b85b3fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://xw.qq.com/iphone/m/caijingzhiku/23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再binc 銀行大班<br />\n<br />\nTrump 如果跟番競選時的政綱，行晒45%關稅，到時就真係中國或贏了<br />\n<br />\n睇住美國加土耳其50%關稅，里拉暴跌，就突然覺得Trump其實加滿中國5500億25%都唔係咩特別事。因為本來就想45%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cba0991e089661656f17563bbd1b2edc3baa66","tid":774930,"uid":25424,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T18:44:40.000Z","msg":"Bin 死左fake news喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7c1e965ccb4344932e236dec37e09aecf0c434","tid":774930,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T18:57:28.000Z","msg":"bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8320b3344a92c457b01df5580ae4f99091f6b884","tid":774930,"uid":33213,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ccae3b9e0aaa52190e899c6eea9ad6bc0c0d4b73","tid":774930,"uid":50457,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"屈宏斌：特朗普對中國進口徵收&ldquo;45%關稅&rdquo;的影響有多大<br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行大中華區首席經濟學家屈宏斌認為，45%的進口關稅可能導致中美雙邊貿易額大幅下降，但對中國整體出口的影響則相對可控。中國政府可能會採取報復性貿易政策應對，並導致部分美國出口產品失去中國市場。中國未來可能更多轉向與其他新興市場地區的貿易和投資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://xw.qq.com/iphone/m/caijingzhiku/23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxw.qq.com%2Fiphone%2Fm%2Fcaijingzhiku%2F23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html&d=64OpQCPjQvKxXoztncByBtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b85b3fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://xw.qq.com/iphone/m/caijingzhiku/23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im