滿中國5500億25%都唔係咩特別事。因為本來就想45%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T19:02:07.000Z","msg":"其實加25%同45%都冇乜分別<br />\n因為支那大部份出口美國嘅利潤得幾個percent<br />\n25%都夠收曬佢地皮<br />\n但係如果支那收同等程度嘅報復性關稅嘅話<br />\n25%關稅嘅損失就細啲<br />\n所以先唔收足45%"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T19:22:31.000Z","msg":"支那人民幣跌左十幾%都唔跳出黎話佢匯率操控國<br />\n擺明侵侵就唔係想開支那拖"},{"pid":"6707337513767895e2e3f23b31822e023bb8e9a1","tid":774930,"uid":50457,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:22:20.000Z","msg":"見到左膠傳媒，同銀行大班奶共奶到唔用腦，個咀臉真係好醜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n匯豐絕對係奶一帶一路最出力的銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347b9fd640b14eece88538c948ada466a61a98e5","tid":774930,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a00a8b523835a16964afec972be1441b9b1b065","tid":774930,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"17年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc5a1c6911f7158af10d03b44864547cf1bdd7b","tid":774930,"uid":26306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:32:13.000Z","msg":"10%加到25%加到45%<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea330b59f998120ecd8b46cbae45a8