id":774930,"uid":33213,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ccae3b9e0aaa52190e899c6eea9ad6bc0c0d4b73","tid":774930,"uid":50457,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"屈宏斌：特朗普對中國進口徵收&ldquo;45%關稅&rdquo;的影響有多大<br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行大中華區首席經濟學家屈宏斌認為，45%的進口關稅可能導致中美雙邊貿易額大幅下降，但對中國整體出口的影響則相對可控。中國政府可能會採取報復性貿易政策應對，並導致部分美國出口產品失去中國市場。中國未來可能更多轉向與其他新興市場地區的貿易和投資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://xw.qq.com/iphone/m/caijingzhiku/23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxw.qq.com%2Fiphone%2Fm%2Fcaijingzhiku%2F23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html&d=64OpQCPjQvKxXoztncByBtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b85b3fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://xw.qq.com/iphone/m/caijingzhiku/23fa59e5bfab83750fc096b71393167d.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再binc 銀行大班<br />\n<br />\nTrump 如果跟番競選時的政綱，行晒45%關稅，到時就真係中國或贏了<br />\n<br />\n睇住美國加土耳其50%關稅，里拉暴跌，就突然覺得Trump其實加滿中國5500億25%都唔係咩特別事。因為本來就想45%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T19:02:07.000Z","msg":"其實加25%同45%都冇乜分別<br />\n因為支那大部份出口美國嘅利潤得幾個percent<br />\n25%都夠收曬佢地皮<br />\n但係如果支那收同等程度嘅報復性關稅嘅話<br />\n25%關稅嘅損失就細啲<br />\n所以先唔收足45%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"你知唔知咩叫關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c6b7c1eddc3fecfb5d2d3b8c7b3dddb2fb9545","tid":774930,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09763c5dfb911941817a685eb518cfdb5339609c","tid":774930,"uid":60529,"like":1,"dislike"